<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="42190000t" end="59440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">为什么会下起大雪…</p>
<p begin="59450000t" end="71980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="112530000t" end="130840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">大家, 发生什么事了</p>
<p begin="134440000t" end="143870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">这场雪是…</p>
<p begin="149660000t" end="172630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">这场雪是不久前开始下的</p>
<p begin="175680000t" end="197540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">不知不觉就积这么厚了</p>
<p begin="204820000t" end="222740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">我们来不及避难</p>
<p begin="226420000t" end="253670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">好险躲在这里才逃过一劫</p>
<p begin="253680000t" end="277380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">这是谁做的呢</p>
<p begin="303250000t" end="334110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">不是爱蜜莉雅大人做的吗</p>
<p begin="341150000t" end="350490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">我吗</p>
<p begin="357520000t" end="365820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">不是的…</p>
<p begin="369650000t" end="387650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">但是, 那个精灵说</p>
<p begin="387660000t" end="395900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">要道谢的话</p>
<p begin="395910000t" end="408750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">就和爱蜜莉雅大人说…</p>
<p begin="408760000t" end="430650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">和莉雅说吧</p>
<p begin="443780000t" end="451980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">…是帕克</p>
<p begin="624460000t" end="655530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">莉雅的工作应该还没做完吧</p>
<p begin="684670000t" end="708230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">各位, 试炼已经结束了</p>
<p begin="713230000t" end="743410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">但是在这样的大雪中移动<br />实在是太危险了</p>
<p begin="749190000t" end="770790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">所以请大家先进墓所中避难吧</p>
<p begin="776320000t" end="783570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">这位先生</p>
<p begin="793200000t" end="806840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">这里可以拜托你吗</p>
<p begin="820360000t" end="826760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">是的</p>
<p begin="830050000t" end="853830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">爱蜜莉雅大人您呢</p>
<p begin="863920000t" end="893310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">我好像必须去那里一趟才行</p>
<p begin="907530000t" end="920610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">你们能平安等我回来吗</p>
<p begin="952100000t" end="982400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">如同试炼前和您约定好的</p>
<p begin="986470000t" end="1000980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">爱蜜莉雅大人才是</p>
<p begin="1000990000t" end="1012050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">请一定要平安</p>
<p begin="1180860000t" end="1190620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">拉姆</p>
<p begin="1201170000t" end="1224060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">看到书被烧掉就失去理智了呢</p>
<p begin="1233360000t" end="1244620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">真不像你啊</p>
<p begin="1252080000t" end="1270810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">不过那孩子早有觉悟了</p>
<p begin="1278000000t" end="1288360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">她是个坚强的孩子</p>
<p begin="1311580000t" end="1348690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">拉姆, 为什么, 你要…</p>
<p begin="1358460000t" end="1398320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">拉姆爱着罗兹瓦尔大人喔</p>
<p begin="1403170000t" end="1416970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">是你输了</p>
<p begin="1416980000t" end="1426980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="1433470000t" end="1453340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">那孩子的目的已经达成了</p>
<p begin="1460990000t" end="1479530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">不惜历经风险呢</p>
<p begin="1497440000t" end="1518250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">再过不久莉雅就会完成试炼</p>
<p begin="1524200000t" end="1540400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">能依靠的书也被销毁了</p>
<p begin="1548910000t" end="1571920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">说实话我真是满佩服你的执着</p>
<p begin="1578720000t" end="1585940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">不过…</p>
<p begin="1611260000t" end="1619790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">…雪</p>
<p begin="1623860000t" end="1636630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">怎么可能</p>
<p begin="1664290000t" end="1674620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">被摆了一道</p>
<p begin="1679540000t" end="1695290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">在战斗之前</p>
<p begin="1695300000t" end="1722000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">就已经准备好呼唤雪云的术式了吗</p>
<p begin="1737790000t" end="1748220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">下大雪了</p>
<p begin="1754440000t" end="1776300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">昴担心的事情还是发生了</p>
<p begin="1786620000t" end="1805850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">我去拖延一些时间吧</p>
<p begin="1835940000t" end="1860000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">罗兹瓦尔, 你真厉害啊</p>
<p begin="1860010000t" end="1876570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">你是个了不起的魔法师</p>
<p begin="1885560000t" end="1898460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">就我所知</p>
<p begin="1898470000t" end="1924950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">应该没有像你这么熟练魔法的人类了吧</p>
<p begin="1941050000t" end="1949380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">不过</p>
<p begin="1953600000t" end="1976100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">无论如何你终究是人类</p>
<p begin="1982200000t" end="2000230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">不可能变得和那个魔人一样的</p>
<p begin="2231170000t" end="2247700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">我已经照睿智之书所写</p>
<p begin="2253640000t" end="2267480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">让大雪降下了</p>
<p begin="2301150000t" end="2317690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">接下来我该怎么办才好</p>
<p begin="2455810000t" end="2465050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">拉姆</p>
<p begin="2488020000t" end="2501430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">对了, 拉姆</p>
<p begin="2591490000t" end="2618820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">老师, 我…</p>
<p begin="2634210000t" end="2644210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">我</p>
<p begin="2663440000t" end="2673900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">我…</p>
<p begin="2673910000t" end="2701360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">我该怎么做才好呢, 老师…</p>
<p begin="2721130000t" end="2732990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">请您再次</p>
<p begin="2738150000t" end="2778640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">引导无知的我吧</p>
<p begin="2786170000t" end="2796140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">老师</p>
<p begin="2879980000t" end="2893570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">玛那在翻腾着</p>
<p begin="2903040000t" end="2931220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">这里就是让大雪降下的原因吗</p>
<p begin="3004030000t" end="3015090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">帕克还在等我</p>
<p begin="3018540000t" end="3026920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">必须快点过去才行</p>
<p begin="3091670000t" end="3102420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">琉…兹?</p>
<p begin="3112970000t" end="3125880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">爱蜜莉雅大人</p>
<p begin="3125890000t" end="3138970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">为什么会来这里…</p>
<p begin="3166930000t" end="3182000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">这么多…</p>
<p begin="3192170000t" end="3232090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">琉兹的妈妈也太辛苦了吧…</p>
<p begin="3232100000t" end="3250620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">关于老朽们复制体的事</p>
<p begin="3250630000t" end="3262400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">晚点再和您说明</p>
<p begin="3262410000t" end="3282770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">总之请快点阻止老朽</p>
<p begin="3287810000t" end="3305090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">阻止…琉兹?</p>
<p begin="3354850000t" end="3370730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">你是希玛对吧</p>
<p begin="3378240000t" end="3411280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">爱蜜莉雅大人会在这里</p>
<p begin="3411290000t" end="3435210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">代表您已经通过试炼了对吧</p>
<p begin="3442170000t" end="3466460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">看来加小鬼是对的呢</p>
<p begin="3473840000t" end="3499130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">那个魔水晶里的是琉兹</p>
<p begin="3503660000t" end="3519900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">你们是为了带那孩子出去吗</p>
<p begin="3526080000t" end="3546200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">只要把大家一起带去墓所就好了吗</p>
<p begin="3557810000t" end="3572690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">真让人傻眼</p>
<p begin="3572700000t" end="3584320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">看到这个状况</p>
<p begin="3584330000t" end="3606000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">你第一个想到的竟然是这个吗</p>
<p begin="3614330000t" end="3628610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">没问题的</p>
<p begin="3633380000t" end="3655370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">用冰做成雪橇坐上去的话</p>
<p begin="3655380000t" end="3676770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">大家一起拉就拉得动了</p>
<p begin="3688730000t" end="3711240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">谢谢你的好意, 不过…</p>
<p begin="3711250000t" end="3730380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">老朽会到这里来</p>
<p begin="3730390000t" end="3758980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">是为了和在魔水晶里沉睡着的始祖</p>
<p begin="3758990000t" end="3780580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">一起完成自己的职责</p>
<p begin="3785590000t" end="3798060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">完成自己的职责?</p>
<p begin="3802670000t" end="3819640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">这个魔水晶</p>
<p begin="3819650000t" end="3846650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">正是覆盖了整个圣域的结界的核心</p>
<p begin="3850410000t" end="3876060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">爱蜜莉雅大人已经将术式解除了</p>
<p begin="3879500000t" end="3901730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">接下来只要失去核心的话</p>
<p begin="3901740000t" end="3924710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">圣域就将结束它的职责</p>
<p begin="3924720000t" end="3938890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">获得解放</p>
<p begin="3949980000t" end="3966470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">顺利的话…呢…</p>
<p begin="3972020000t" end="4008770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">那个…不一定非得现在不可吧</p>
<p begin="4008780000t" end="4032730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">外面的雪下得超大的…</p>
<p begin="4032740000t" end="4057760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">万一设施被破坏</p>
<p begin="4057770000t" end="4079680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">或是少了管理者</p>
<p begin="4079690000t" end="4101800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">就会变成无法挽回的局面</p>
<p begin="4106330000t" end="4132520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">而老朽们就是为此而存在的钥匙</p>
<p begin="4208210000t" end="4231750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">爱蜜莉雅大人, 这个…</p>
<p begin="4269880000t" end="4282150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">是帕克吗</p>
<p begin="4286170000t" end="4318690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">大精灵大人早一步造访了这里</p>
<p begin="4318700000t" end="4340600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">并成功拖延了术式发动的时间</p>
<p begin="4343970000t" end="4366350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">为了拯救大家而拼尽全力</p>
<p begin="4366360000t" end="4388260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">力量也消耗殆尽了</p>
<p begin="4392480000t" end="4410720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">做出那些冰壁</p>
<p begin="4416580000t" end="4438680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">在大雪降下时保护大家</p>
<p begin="4447910000t" end="4477110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">为了告诉我这里的位置而勉强自己…</p>
<p begin="4485010000t" end="4514370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">其他还不知道又做了多少乱来的事情…</p>
<p begin="4521020000t" end="4546840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">借用了许多的力量</p>
<p begin="4546850000t" end="4559870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">而如果这个结果</p>
<p begin="4565260000t" end="4590880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">带来了如此机会的话</p>
<p begin="4595890000t" end="4629090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">老朽也应该尽老朽们的职责才对</p>
<p begin="4636900000t" end="4651800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">职责的话老朽懂</p>
<p begin="4651810000t" end="4659410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">不过…</p>
<p begin="4659420000t" end="4669240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">这十年</p>
<p begin="4669250000t" end="4697660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">老朽一直和可爱的孙子朝夕相处</p>
<p begin="4702000000t" end="4728610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">加菲…老朽的孙子</p>
<p begin="4728620000t" end="4755020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">挺起胸膛地说要到外面去</p>
<p begin="4759790000t" end="4790090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">而老朽也愿意多推他一把</p>
<p begin="4796420000t" end="4824010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">不过接下来还要麻烦你们看着他了</p>
<p begin="4829090000t" end="4858800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">身为老朽另一半的姐妹们啊</p>
<p begin="4969960000t" end="4979940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">接下来的事</p>
<p begin="4985180000t" end="4992500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">就交给我吧</p>
<p begin="5019840000t" end="5053710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">仅仅半日就有这么惊人的成长</p>
<p begin="5058790000t" end="5072350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">看来只有这部分</p>
<p begin="5072360000t" end="5094350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">是年长者的乐趣所在吧</p>
<p begin="5365500000t" end="5381390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">走吧, 琉兹</p>
<p begin="5388740000t" end="5416530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">我们还有必须完成的事</p>
<p begin="5421300000t" end="5435280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">爱蜜莉雅大人…</p>
<p begin="5445760000t" end="5464370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">因为有被托付的思念</p>
<p begin="5468830000t" end="5485710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">有希望达成的心愿</p>
<p begin="5497510000t" end="5517700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">所以晚点再哭吧</p>
<p begin="5523390000t" end="5540460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">我所喜欢的人们</p>
<p begin="5540470000t" end="5559000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">一直都是笑着这么跟我说的</p>
<p begin="5598390000t" end="5614390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">拜托了, 请告诉我</p>
<p begin="5620800000t" end="5637480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">拉姆和罗兹瓦尔在哪里</p>
<p begin="5780920000t" end="5795480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">拉姆, 罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="5849150000t" end="5862760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">等等, 罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="5862770000t" end="5880880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">不能继续待在这里</p>
<p begin="5880890000t" end="5897250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">现在可不是冻僵的时候啊</p>
<p begin="5956940000t" end="5964060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">拉姆</p>
<p begin="5975870000t" end="5995330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">拉姆, 拉姆</p>
<p begin="6032980000t" end="6042790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">还活着</p>
<p begin="6042800000t" end="6049460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">没事</p>
<p begin="6049470000t" end="6059320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">还来得及</p>
<p begin="6063780000t" end="6072530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="6095190000t" end="6114010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">你救了拉姆吧</p>
<p begin="6120110000t" end="6129460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">罗兹瓦尔</p>
<p begin="6129470000t" end="6150420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">总之带着拉姆跟我一起走吧</p>
<p begin="6153410000t" end="6171410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">我会努力的, 不要放弃…</p>
<p begin="6173750000t" end="6185820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">算了…</p>
<p begin="6208710000t" end="6221570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">已经…够了…</p>
<p begin="6253530000t" end="6270530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">不要说这种任性的话</p>
<p begin="6276820000t" end="6298630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">说算了是怎么回事</p>
<p begin="6298640000t" end="6318540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">才不能就这样算了</p>
<p begin="6322130000t" end="6333890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">不要擅自放弃</p>
<p begin="6333900000t" end="6348240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">自作主张的结束</p>
<p begin="6352330000t" end="6358470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">不管是我</p>
<p begin="6358480000t" end="6364300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">还是拉姆</p>
<p begin="6364310000t" end="6372330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">甚至是你</p>
<p begin="6376050000t" end="6384590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">我们没有一个人</p>
<p begin="6384600000t" end="6405470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">应该在这里结束</p>
<p begin="6411020000t" end="6433530000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">我通过了试炼</p>
<p begin="6433540000t" end="6453480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">不管是害怕着的过去</p>
<p begin="6453490000t" end="6475700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">原本应该要变得幸福的现在</p>
<p begin="6475710000t" end="6500710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">还是有一天可能<br />会造访的悲伤的未来</p>
<p begin="6500720000t" end="6513940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">我全部都看见了</p>
<p begin="6513950000t" end="6523650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">即使如此</p>
<p begin="6523660000t" end="6535780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">我还是决定</p>
<p begin="6535790000t" end="6548970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">踏上了这条路</p>
<p begin="6553340000t" end="6573480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">我总算是能够向前迈进了</p>
<p begin="6627000000t" end="6645640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">和别人说话的时候</p>
<p begin="6645650000t" end="6673110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">要好好看着对方的脸才行</p>
<p begin="6693040000t" end="6705910000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">我不会让任何人</p>
<p begin="6705920000t" end="6719070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">说已经够了这种话</p>
<p begin="6723370000t" end="6734750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">只要还活着</p>
<p begin="6734760000t" end="6757050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">就不该说出这种话</p>
<p begin="6763460000t" end="6772290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">所以</p>
<p begin="6772300000t" end="6809670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">我是不会放弃任何一个人的</p>
<p begin="6889660000t" end="6899710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">跟过来了</p>
<p begin="6904410000t" end="6927680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">是因为我是魔女吗</p>
<p begin="6935190000t" end="6963540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">还是因为帕克在这里呢</p>
<p begin="7046270000t" end="7062260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">罗兹瓦尔和拉姆就拜托你们了</p>
<p begin="7100860000t" end="7111990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">等回到墓所…</p>
<p begin="7118560000t" end="7140450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">我一定会保护大家的</p>
<p begin="7231540000t" end="7258800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">贝蒂会开始等待"那个人"出现</p>
<p begin="7258810000t" end="7275180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">是在失去了琉兹</p>
<p begin="7278390000t" end="7300040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">并以她的存在作为交换</p>
<p begin="7300050000t" end="7337080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">创造出"圣域"不久后的事情</p>
<p begin="7388610000t" end="7399230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="7404550000t" end="7441140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">我的知识书库就交给你来管理了</p>
<p begin="7455680000t" end="7477380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">直到下次的时机来临前</p>
<p begin="7477390000t" end="7492870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">希望你做好书库的管理者</p>
<p begin="7492880000t" end="7513520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">好好守护这些知识</p>
<p begin="7530400000t" end="7559710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">对了, 就称呼为"禁书库"吧</p>
<p begin="7564790000t" end="7606930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">那里把我拥有的知识都化为书籍</p>
<p begin="7606940000t" end="7616960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">保管起来了</p>
<p begin="7620950000t" end="7631470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">等…等等…</p>
<p begin="7631480000t" end="7662260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">书库就和罗兹瓦尔的宅邸<br />相连在一起吧</p>
<p begin="7666270000t" end="7674760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">那孩子的话</p>
<p begin="7674770000t" end="7692790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">一定能成为你的助力的</p>
<p begin="7692800000t" end="7709080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">稍微等一等</p>
<p begin="7715180000t" end="7730470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">我不明白您所说的</p>
<p begin="7730480000t" end="7744770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">禁书库什么的</p>
<p begin="7744780000t" end="7761290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">贝蒂要和母亲大人一起…</p>
<p begin="7761300000t" end="7772660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">很可惜的</p>
<p begin="7772670000t" end="7789280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">连罗兹瓦尔都无法击败的敌人</p>
<p begin="7789290000t" end="7808970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">你就算一起战斗也是没用的</p>
<p begin="7814200000t" end="7839490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">如果我和你都一起被消灭了</p>
<p begin="7839500000t" end="7856740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">那知识的累积该怎么办呢</p>
<p begin="7861270000t" end="7884090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">我有把这些知识传承下去的义务</p>
<p begin="7890580000t" end="7916930000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">该不会…贝蒂的力量</p>
<p begin="7916940000t" end="7935280000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">是为了这种时候…</p>
<p begin="7953800000t" end="7978700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">母亲大人您…从一开始就全都…</p>
<p begin="8027070000t" end="8035460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">这是…</p>
<p begin="8040240000t" end="8077600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">这是赋予我的权能"睿智之书"的</p>
<p begin="8077610000t" end="8099680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">不完全的复制品</p>
<p begin="8105700000t" end="8119230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">但应该能为持有者的未来</p>
<p begin="8119240000t" end="8141330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">做出简单的指引</p>
<p begin="8156420000t" end="8168720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">书有2本</p>
<p begin="8173720000t" end="8187270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">1本给你</p>
<p begin="8187280000t" end="8211640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">而另一本已经交给罗兹瓦尔了</p>
<p begin="8215940000t" end="8226860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">虽然很抱歉</p>
<p begin="8226870000t" end="8240670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">但希望你们能理解</p>
<p begin="8253650000t" end="8269080000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">说一下关于期限的事吧</p>
<p begin="8276190000t" end="8295340000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">如果我没有回来的话</p>
<p begin="8300340000t" end="8330290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">总有一天会有一位<br />有资格继承我知识的人</p>
<p begin="8330300000t" end="8349920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">来迎接你的</p>
<p begin="8349930000t" end="8368860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">迎接…贝蒂…</p>
<p begin="8368870000t" end="8395130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">假设, 就称为"那个人"吧</p>
<p begin="8399670000t" end="8415840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">请你等待"那个人"出现</p>
<p begin="8415850000t" end="8429090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">那就是我</p>
<p begin="8429100000t" end="8443400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">最后的愿望了</p>
<p begin="8473010000t" end="8481840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">贝蒂…</p>
<p begin="8494900000t" end="8505050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">至少要</p>
<p begin="8505060000t" end="8517010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">好好活下去</p>
<p begin="8585830000t" end="8605820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">贝蒂照母亲大人的嘱咐</p>
<p begin="8605830000t" end="8636290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">躲在罗兹瓦尔宅邸当中</p>
<p begin="8636300000t" end="8653690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">做出了"禁书库"</p>
<p begin="8653700000t" end="8668130000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">并称呼自己为"管理员"</p>
<p begin="8677050000t" end="8688260000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">不知道什么时候开始</p>
<p begin="8688270000t" end="8727410000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">罗兹瓦尔开始频繁地进出这里</p>
<p begin="8746170000t" end="8771300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">今天也要稍微打扰一下啰</p>
<p begin="8783260000t" end="8809170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">复制…灵魂…</p>
<p begin="8809180000t" end="8841090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">-并覆盖掉…原有的器皿…<br />-他的目的只是书架上的知识</p>
<p begin="8841100000t" end="8867420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">我们几乎没有交谈</p>
<p begin="8893050000t" end="8914890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">初次见面, 碧翠丝大人</p>
<p begin="8923100000t" end="8933760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">我从上一代那里</p>
<p begin="8933770000t" end="8962200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">听过您的事情了</p>
<p begin="8974540000t" end="8985110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">请您安心</p>
<p begin="8991910000t" end="9020000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">作为当代的罗兹瓦尔·B·梅札斯</p>
<p begin="9024300000t" end="9036640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">您的职责</p>
<p begin="9041880000t" end="9064010000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">与令堂的恩情都会由我继承下来</p>
<p begin="9077610000t" end="9091390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">宅邸的管理</p>
<p begin="9091400000t" end="9109190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">将会由继承了罗兹瓦尔名号</p>
<p begin="9109200000t" end="9134110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">的梅札斯一族来执行</p>
<p begin="9144190000t" end="9153670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">在那之后</p>
<p begin="9153680000t" end="9168020000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">400年间</p>
<p begin="9171570000t" end="9192240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">我们几乎没有需要对谈的事情</p>
<p begin="9226650000t" end="9257100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">曾经也有一些人来到禁书库</p>
<p begin="9257110000t" end="9275600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">希望带贝蒂一起走</p>
<p begin="9283810000t" end="9300590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">但是最后都没有成真</p>
<p begin="9314190000t" end="9342680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">和憧憬的哥哥无预警地再会时</p>
<p begin="9342690000t" end="9361760000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">我的内心久违地起了涟漪</p>
<p begin="9368800000t" end="9385380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">但是也马上就注意到</p>
<p begin="9394130000t" end="9408670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">自己和哥哥是不一样的</p>
<p begin="9418910000t" end="9440730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">被羡慕和嫉妒所驱使</p>
<p begin="9440740000t" end="9470030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">为了不伤害和他在一起的半魔小姑娘</p>
<p begin="9470040000t" end="9484500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">我扼杀了自己的感情</p>
<p begin="9484510000t" end="9497870000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">并不再说话</p>
<p begin="9511240000t" end="9528420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">就在那时候</p>
<p begin="9528430000t" end="9545960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">发现第一个村民啦</p>
<p begin="9549630000t" end="9564920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">异物就这样唐突地</p>
<p begin="9564930000t" end="9573610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">毫无顾虑地</p>
<p begin="9573620000t" end="9591230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">直接踩了进来</p>
<p begin="9599750000t" end="9621690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">-碧翠子, 碧翠子<br />-不知怎么地就这样留在宅邸中</p>
<p begin="9627640000t" end="9660860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">这个男人的态度<br />与先前来过禁书库的人完全不同</p>
<p begin="9665030000t" end="9710380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">我也曾想过他会不会<br />就是母亲说的"那个人"呢</p>
<p begin="9738080000t" end="9771200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">因为害怕这渺小的期待会被背叛</p>
<p begin="9776750000t" end="9798610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">所以我照着罗兹瓦尔的意愿</p>
<p begin="9798620000t" end="9816150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">把他送往了"圣域"</p>
<p begin="9827250000t" end="9849140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">要去见"强欲的魔女"</p>
<p begin="9856100000t" end="9888790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">留下这句话的罗兹瓦尔前往了"圣域"</p>
<p begin="9888800000t" end="9915750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">我明白他是要去做个了结</p>
<p begin="9924740000t" end="9935880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">那贝蒂呢</p>
<p begin="9943930000t" end="9954470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">空白的书</p>
<p begin="9959160000t" end="9984150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">约定的那个人从未造访过</p>
<p begin="9990400000t" end="10001830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">我总算知道了</p>
<p begin="10008400000t" end="10040840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">"那个人"永远都不会来到这里</p>
<p begin="10050620000t" end="10067420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">明明从很久以前我就知道了</p>
<p begin="10073130000t" end="10083750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">但是…</p>
<p begin="10083760000t" end="10105710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">我要带你出去, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="10110800000t" end="10123450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">这次我一定会</p>
<p begin="10123460000t" end="10147980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">手牵手把你拉出去走到太阳下</p>
<p begin="10147990000t" end="10160050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">你愿意成为</p>
<p begin="10166070000t" end="10198040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">贝蒂的…"那个人"吗</p>
<p begin="10198050000t" end="10211220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">你是笨蛋吗</p>
<p begin="10211230000t" end="10223160000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">我怎么可能会</p>
<p begin="10223170000t" end="10230940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">是你那个什么</p>
<p begin="10263580000t" end="10285220000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">我已经累了</p>
<p begin="10377260000t" end="10386400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">可恶</p>
<p begin="10386410000t" end="10400750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">你在哪里, 碧翠子</p>
<p begin="10572300000t" end="10593950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">干脆就这样…</p>
<p begin="10600440000t" end="10619140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">总算回来了</p>
<p begin="10619150000t" end="10629810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">你这个大笨蛋</p>
<p begin="10629820000t" end="10640490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">你刚刚竟然敢</p>
<p begin="10666980000t" end="10691660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">明明就是你自己结束对话的</p>
<p begin="10696750000t" end="10723390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">怎么还这么恬不知耻</p>
<p begin="10729790000t" end="10743880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">给我差不多一点</p>
<p begin="10746930000t" end="10763620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">你这疯小鬼</p>
<p begin="10763630000t" end="10791500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">-马上就诉诸暴力的话要怎样对话…<br />-你才要差不多一点</p>
<p begin="10850250000t" end="10866540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">撑住了</p>
<p begin="10866550000t" end="10881920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">真是不死心</p>
<p begin="10881930000t" end="10911400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">只要你不是真心拒绝我</p>
<p begin="10911410000t" end="10929440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">不管几次我都会来的</p>
<p begin="10936790000t" end="10947370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">贝蒂可是认真地要把你…</p>
<p begin="10947380000t" end="10960120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">不, 不对</p>
<p begin="10960130000t" end="10974140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">如果你是认真的</p>
<p begin="10974150000t" end="11001610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">我怎么可能还来得了这么多次</p>
<p begin="11001620000t" end="11021750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">你的拒绝不过只是表面而已</p>
<p begin="11076660000t" end="11102110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">你…你这个人</p>
<p begin="11102120000t" end="11118720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">才不是贝蒂的"那个人"</p>
<p begin="11123720000t" end="11150890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">你自己也说了不是吧</p>
<p begin="11150900000t" end="11181980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">你说了对吧</p>
<p begin="11188860000t" end="11207440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">如果你就是"那个人"的话</p>
<p begin="11213700000t" end="11233970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">即使是谎言, 只要你这样对我说的话</p>
<p begin="11238270000t" end="11261490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">贝蒂也一定会相信的吧</p>
<p begin="11268020000t" end="11281790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">因为即使知道是谎言</p>
<p begin="11281800000t" end="11299500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">我也只能相信了啊</p>
<p begin="11313100000t" end="11325700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="11332810000t" end="11364110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">但是你说了你不是</p>
<p begin="11372160000t" end="11382150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">才不是</p>
<p begin="11382160000t" end="11393000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">你是笨蛋吗</p>
<p begin="11393010000t" end="11405110000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">你就是这么说的</p>
<p begin="11408660000t" end="11420630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">贝蒂就是笨</p>
<p begin="11420640000t" end="11430470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">大笨蛋</p>
<p begin="11430480000t" end="11466670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">都是因为无法忘记<br />400年前那句口头的承诺…</p>
<p begin="11472930000t" end="11479720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">所以</p>
<p begin="11483470000t" end="11495820000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">现在不管你说什么</p>
<p begin="11495830000t" end="11510050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">都已经结束了</p>
<p begin="11586610000t" end="11595120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">我</p>
<p begin="11636610000t" end="11668040000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">我才不是你的什么"那个人"</p>
<p begin="11668050000t" end="11684740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">不管几次我的答案都一样</p>
<p begin="11709910000t" end="11718630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">但是</p>
<p begin="11743090000t" end="11768950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">我想和你在一起啊</p>
<p begin="11768960000t" end="11778810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="11801940000t" end="11826730000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">为了让温柔的你不再悲伤</p>
<p begin="11837370000t" end="11855030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">我想待在你身边</p>
<p begin="12018840000t" end="12027380000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">怎么了</p>
<p begin="12122780000t" end="12134750000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="12183890000t" end="12192370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">完…</p>
<p begin="12285880000t" end="12302660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">宅邸的玄关吗</p>
<p begin="12302670000t" end="12329170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">就这样给我滚去的意思啊</p>
<p begin="12352140000t" end="12374590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">如果宅邸的门都烧毁的话</p>
<p begin="12384760000t" end="12399610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">那家伙的禁书库就…</p>
<p begin="12408290000t" end="12419230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">永别了</p>
<p begin="12426030000t" end="12444350000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">什么永别啊</p>
<p begin="12447170000t" end="12481300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">谁会让你用这种形式结束啊</p>
<p begin="12551750000t" end="12570860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">已经没有其他门了</p>
<p begin="12610710000t" end="12624190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">不对, 还没…</p>
<p begin="12836980000t" end="12847420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="12852270000t" end="12864720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">如果你听得到的话</p>
<p begin="12864730000t" end="12874600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">就仔细听好了</p>
<p begin="12893900000t" end="12913230000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">已经没有其他门了</p>
<p begin="12919630000t" end="12938980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">这是最后一扇了</p>
<p begin="12946720000t" end="12964850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">如果打开这扇门</p>
<p begin="12964860000t" end="12980710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">我或许就会死吧</p>
<p begin="13065240000t" end="13076310000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="13084740000t" end="13107190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">我相信你</p>
<p begin="13236630000t" end="13254070000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">你真的是个笨蛋呢</p>
<p begin="13260010000t" end="13285740000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">一开口竟然就是那句喔</p>
<p begin="13291520000t" end="13305690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">因为就是那样不是吗</p>
<p begin="13313890000t" end="13334170000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">这样就陷入僵局了呢</p>
<p begin="13350500000t" end="13372640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">不过贝蒂也不多求什么</p>
<p begin="13379990000t" end="13395420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">因为我已经完全违反</p>
<p begin="13395430000t" end="13415140000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">和母亲大人的约定了</p>
<p begin="13426630000t" end="13436610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">这样的话</p>
<p begin="13454430000t" end="13478640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">最后听我说一句吧</p>
<p begin="13526130000t" end="13537200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="13543220000t" end="13560630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">帮助我吧</p>
<p begin="13583220000t" end="13612630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">我要把你从孤独里带出来</p>
<p begin="13612640000t" end="13644900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">这种帅气无比的话我想了很多</p>
<p begin="13651940000t" end="13687270000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">但那其实全都只是一股劲地<br />想赶快敷衍了事的内容罢了</p>
<p begin="13699150000t" end="13714610000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">说什么要帮助你</p>
<p begin="13718470000t" end="13747490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">其实你应该根本不需要我的力量</p>
<p begin="13753830000t" end="13769830000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">你既强悍</p>
<p begin="13769840000t" end="13787200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">聪明又可爱</p>
<p begin="13797280000t" end="13831560000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">你有着足够让自己一个人<br />生存下去的力量</p>
<p begin="13836330000t" end="13842840000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">所以</p>
<p begin="13846750000t" end="13866450000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">只说要帮助你或成为你的助力</p>
<p begin="13866460000t" end="13885860000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">这种话你根本听不进去</p>
<p begin="13890870000t" end="13926100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">但是就算是既强悍又聪明可爱的你</p>
<p begin="13930250000t" end="13949090000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">也害怕一个人活着</p>
<p begin="13954410000t" end="13979810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">因为那很辛苦, 又寂寞对吧</p>
<p begin="13991300000t" end="14024540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">所以你会想依靠"那个人"的存在</p>
<p begin="14028460000t" end="14042030000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">也没有人会责怪的</p>
<p begin="14050470000t" end="14068250000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">少…少擅自…</p>
<p begin="14072550000t" end="14100720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">明明拒绝了贝蒂</p>
<p begin="14114230000t" end="14132550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">你又知道贝蒂些什么了</p>
<p begin="14176530000t" end="14192780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">我知道的</p>
<p begin="14198330000t" end="14215710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">你很温柔</p>
<p begin="14221960000t" end="14244320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">如果有人被恶梦纠缠着</p>
<p begin="14244330000t" end="14274950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle420">你会握着他的手让他安心</p>
<p begin="14279060000t" end="14295360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle421">少说得好像你知道什么一样</p>
<p begin="14295370000t" end="14312630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle422">没有力量的我</p>
<p begin="14312640000t" end="14332970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle423">没办法成为你的助力</p>
<p begin="14343440000t" end="14364300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle424">即使这样也不想让你孤单一人的我</p>
<p begin="14364390000t" end="14381400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle425">所能做得到的事</p>
<p begin="14390380000t" end="14415470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle426">也就只有紧抓着再三恳求你了吧</p>
<p begin="14493910000t" end="14504000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle427">碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="14507520000t" end="14526980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle428">请帮助我吧</p>
<p begin="14540110000t" end="14578650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle429">请帮助如果你不在了<br />会因为寂寞活不下去的我吧</p>
<p begin="14599200000t" end="14610710000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle430">太狡猾</p>
<p begin="14630010000t" end="14643570000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle431">太狡猾了…</p>
<p begin="14649350000t" end="14663980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle432">那种讲法</p>
<p begin="14671720000t" end="14706630000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle433">因为…你又不是"那个人"</p>
<p begin="14716090000t" end="14736200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle434">明明就拒绝了贝蒂</p>
<p begin="14775000000t" end="14784210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle435">但是</p>
<p begin="14795010000t" end="14805210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle436">400年</p>
<p begin="14805220000t" end="14820460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle437">我一直都是一个人</p>
<p begin="14834450000t" end="14859850000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle438">就算在这里牵起你的手</p>
<p begin="14859860000t" end="14885120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle439">你也会马上死去的</p>
<p begin="14894580000t" end="14910780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle440">人类的寿命</p>
<p begin="14915870000t" end="14943060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle441">对贝蒂来说只是转瞬之间而已</p>
<p begin="14952910000t" end="14960490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle442">事到如今</p>
<p begin="14960500000t" end="14976950000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle443">要依靠这种东西什么的…</p>
<p begin="14976960000t" end="14983800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle444">但是</p>
<p begin="14987840000t" end="15020240000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle445">你和我能够一起携手走向明天</p>
<p begin="15030790000t" end="15057390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle446">明天, 后天, 大后天</p>
<p begin="15068330000t" end="15086060000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle447">就算无法跟你一起400年之久</p>
<p begin="15090120000t" end="15124890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle448">不过接下来的每一天我都会和你一起</p>
<p begin="15130210000t" end="15149970000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle449">即使不是永远</p>
<p begin="15153650000t" end="15169940000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle450">但明天还有现在</p>
<p begin="15169950000t" end="15189180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle451">我都会好好对待你的</p>
<p begin="15210520000t" end="15230890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle452">所以, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="15252370000t" end="15269390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle453">选择我吧</p>
<p begin="15283220000t" end="15294640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle454">你…</p>
<p begin="15294650000t" end="15311120000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle455">才不是"那个人"…</p>
<p begin="15311130000t" end="15319390000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle456">的确不是</p>
<p begin="15324160000t" end="15334880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle457">我就是我</p>
<p begin="15334890000t" end="15348000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle458">菜月昴</p>
<p begin="15352150000t" end="15384780000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle459">把这400年你对根本没见过面的家伙</p>
<p begin="15384790000t" end="15400470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle460">的单相思给忘了吧</p>
<p begin="15414930000t" end="15448550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle461">与其害怕总有一天会来临的离别</p>
<p begin="15448560000t" end="15469420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle462">不如和我一起活着迎接</p>
<p begin="15469430000t" end="15485460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle463">一定会来临的明天吧</p>
<p begin="15492880000t" end="15504790000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle464">虽然我很弱</p>
<p begin="15509720000t" end="15528980000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle465">但总是过分奢求</p>
<p begin="15534300000t" end="15548800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle466">所以和我一起的话</p>
<p begin="15548810000t" end="15572660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle467">爱管闲事的你一定会忙到不行</p>
<p begin="15572670000t" end="15608600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle468">连觉得无聊或寂寞的时间都没有</p>
<p begin="15629960000t" end="15650210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle469">选择我吧, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="15658100000t" end="15681660000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle470">明明就会消失…</p>
<p begin="15681670000t" end="15696550000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle471">世上没有永远的事</p>
<p begin="15699990000t" end="15715890000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle472">你所害怕的未来</p>
<p begin="15715900000t" end="15731650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle473">总有一天一定会来临</p>
<p begin="15734540000t" end="15744370000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle474">即使如此…</p>
<p begin="15744380000t" end="15764300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle475">明明就会抛下我</p>
<p begin="15764310000t" end="15784700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle476">即使如此也和我在一起吧</p>
<p begin="15788380000t" end="15802690000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle477">一起试着活下去</p>
<p begin="15802700000t" end="15816540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle478">一起走下去吧</p>
<p begin="15822880000t" end="15850180000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle479">让我们一起去累积</p>
<p begin="15850190000t" end="15870720000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle480">快乐到能理直气壮笑出来的回忆吧</p>
<p begin="15876960000t" end="15890210000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle481">把你在这四百年中</p>
<p begin="15890220000t" end="15911920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle482">所度过的寂寞全部补回</p>
<p begin="15911930000t" end="15926600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle483">还绰绰有余的程度</p>
<p begin="15940200000t" end="15969640000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle484">就算做了那种事</p>
<p begin="15978370000t" end="15998540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle485">最后还是会变回一个人</p>
<p begin="16002010000t" end="16022490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle486">对于能永远活下去的你</p>
<p begin="16026880000t" end="16046200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle487">和我度过的时间</p>
<p begin="16046210000t" end="16063620000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle488">或许不过是一瞬间罢了</p>
<p begin="16069550000t" end="16112150000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle489">那么就将我的一瞬间</p>
<p begin="16120230000t" end="16135810000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle490">烙印在你的灵魂上吧</p>
<p begin="16155340000t" end="16173670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle491">菜月昴这个男人</p>
<p begin="16177360000t" end="16194460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle492">是即使在永远的时间当中</p>
<p begin="16194470000t" end="16211650000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle493">也绝不会褪色的</p>
<p begin="16211660000t" end="16236520000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle494">鲜明又强烈的男人啊</p>
<p begin="16270740000t" end="16289960000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle495">选择我吧, 碧翠丝</p>
<p begin="16309150000t" end="16333460000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle496">你不正是因为希望有人能带你出去</p>
<p begin="16333550000t" end="16349190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle497">才会一直</p>
<p begin="16349200000t" end="16374670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle498">坐在门前的吗</p>
<p begin="16578090000t" end="16594500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle499">-奥托先生, 那个是…<br />-好痛</p>
<p begin="16748400000t" end="16759430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle500">昴</p>
<p begin="16759440000t" end="16775190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle501">是我</p>
<p begin="16779780000t" end="16799540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle502">昴, 昴</p>
<p begin="16799550000t" end="16819290000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle503">是啊, 那是我的名字</p>
<p begin="16824680000t" end="16855480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle504">昴, 昴, 昴</p>
<p begin="16860720000t" end="16868500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle505">昴</p>
<p begin="16872560000t" end="16889990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle506">终于肯喊出我的名字了啊</p>
<p begin="16995340000t" end="17011770000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle507">绝对, 绝对</p>
<p begin="17016770000t" end="17045330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle508">不会再失去任何人了</p>
<p begin="17073150000t" end="17091680000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle509">不论是母亲大人, 修斯</p>
<p begin="17096600000t" end="17113050000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle510">还是今天正活在当下的大家</p>
<p begin="17117430000t" end="17145430000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle511">而且, 只要我还没忘记</p>
<p begin="17145440000t" end="17161880000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle512">那个人写给我的话语</p>
<p begin="17161890000t" end="17181420000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle513">我就绝不会放弃的</p>
<p begin="17226190000t" end="17251440000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle514">不用这么勉强自己也没关系喔</p>
<p begin="17255630000t" end="17266580000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle515">爱蜜莉雅酱</p>
<p begin="17345410000t" end="17360490000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle516">接下来就交给我吧</p>
<p begin="17360500000t" end="17376670000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle517">你可以先退下了</p>
<p begin="17380630000t" end="17400480000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle518">因为救援的友军已经来了</p>
<p begin="17413460000t" end="17420470000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle519">对不起</p>
<p begin="17425320000t" end="17444900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle520">我有点听不懂你的意思</p>
<p begin="17537870000t" end="17545540000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle521">真是的</p>
<p begin="17545550000t" end="17564320000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle522">会变成怎样我可不管啰</p>
<p begin="17589790000t" end="17608360000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle523">我跟你的话</p>
<p begin="17621110000t" end="17643330000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle524">一定会有办法的啦</p>
<p begin="17652300000t" end="17699920000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle525">(选择我吧)</p>
</div>
